    <title>Success and Failure of Blockchain Technology Providers: Founders' Power, Beyond‐Blockchain Exploration and Centralized Decision‐Making</title>
    <updated>2025-03-25T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Yuanzhu Zhan, Andy C. L. Yeung, Kim Hua Tan, Yu Xiong, Xinjie Xing, Fei Ye</name>
