    <title>EXPRESS: What Do We Know about the Science of Science in Business and Economics? Insights from the Top 50 Journals, 2008-2022</title>
    <updated>2025-04-04T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Sunil Mithas, Alysson Silveira, Gleb Zavadskiy</name>
